===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} A [[colorless]] and [[inert]] gas, and the second lightest chemical [[element]] (''symbol'' He) with an [[atomic number]] of 2 and [[atomic weight]] of 4.002602.
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A form or sample of the element.

